@node INTRODUCTION "Introduction"

				  @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

With MuiIconType, you can change icons type. You can choice among:

Disk
Kick (for Kickstart disk)
Drawer 
Garbage
Tool
Project

It  does  a  little job, so in my opinion it doesn't need a lot of menus or
other misc functions, and I've implemented only the essential.

@endnode
