Thanks to Simone Tellini for his aid.

@endnode
@node USAGE "Usage"

				     @{b}@{u}Usage@{uu}@{ub}



MuiIconType  usage is very simple:  run it and drag & drop an icon over its
windows, then select the new icon type and press "Convert".

MuiIconType  shows  the  original  icon  type  when dropping an icon in its
window.

At  the  moment, MuiIconType doesn't accept any CLI argument.  Maybe in the
future I'll add a ReadArgs() routine.  Let @{" me " link AUTHOR} know if you want this.

@endnode
